Heat 1/4 cup of the dressing in large nonstick skillet. Add pepper and onion; cook and stir on medium-high heat 3 to 5 min. or until tender. Add asparagus to skillet. Pour remaining 1/4 cup dressing evenly over asparagus; cover. Reduce heat to medium-low; cook 5 to 7 min. or until asparagus are tender. Spoon onto serving platter; sprinkle with cheese.